(62, 'Aluminium Stearate', 'aluminium-stearate-manufacturers', 'Leading Aluminium Stearate manufacturer, supplier in India', 'We are a certified company manufacturing & supplying  Aluminium Stearate from the last 44 years in India, offering best quality we also export over 43 countries', '<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n	{\r\n	  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n	  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\r\n	  \"mainEntity\": [{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"What is the benefit of using Aluminium Stearate?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>Aluminium Stearate is mainly used as gelling agent, used in the manufacturing of grease, oil drilling chemicals, explosives, water proofing of canvas in combination with paraffin wax and also as an anti-selling agent in paints. It also finds use as a gelling agent in pharmaceutical and cosmetic preparations for which we manufacture pharma grade product also. As a <b> leading Aluminium Stearate exporters in India</b>, we strictly control and manage all links related to product quality, establish scientific inspection standards, and ensure that the company maintains stable and qualified products. </p> \"\r\n		}\r\n	  },{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"Where can I purchase premium quality aluminium stearate for industrial purposes? \",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>Store zinc stearate in a cool and ventilated warehouse. Keep away from fire and heat sources. It should be stored separately from oxidants and acids, and avoid mixed storage, equipped with the appropriate variety and quantity of fire equipment. The storage area should be equipped with suitable materials to contain the leakage. </p> \"\r\n	\r\n	  }\r\n	  },{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"What type of aluminium stearate do you supply?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>As one of the<b> Aluminium Stearate manufacturers in the World</b>, at MLA Group, we provide fine quality Aluminium Stearate, available in different forms as per the needs of our customers. Our product, a white fine powder with moisture level less than 2 percent, is stored in fine conditions, out of human touch. We develop them using effective technology backed with strong scientific research. These chemicals are tested on several different quality standards and are inspected strictly in accordance with the procedures.</p> \"\r\n	\r\n		}\r\n	  }]\r\n	}\r\n	</script>', 'product-image/ALSTR.webp', '', '17', 'Unpublished', '<h3>Aluminium Stearate Supplier in India</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries, with an installed capacity of 5000 tons per month for various stearates, is one of the largest manufacturers worldwide for metallic stearates for over 40 years. We are a&nbsp;<strong>leading Aluminium Stearate manufacturers in India&nbsp;</strong>who believe in stringent quality and customer service norms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our company is formed by industry veterans, backed with in-house application labs and independent research and development, production facility, three-tier quality inspection, sales support, worldwide distributor network and strong technical support. We have strict control on raw materials, and ensure that all incoming materials must meet laid down standards, and have establish strict process control parameters. A&nbsp;<strong>Leading Aluminium Stearate supplier in the world&nbsp;</strong>, we have a production capacity of more than 400 tons per month, which is one of the largest worldwide. We actively listen to customer needs; carefully build product quality, sincerely provide services; and truly believe that serving the customers is the sole reason for our existence.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product: Aluminium Stearate</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Aluminium Stearate is a white or slightly yellow powder, mainly used as a heat stabilizer and lubricant for PVC plastics, anti-settling agent and drier in the paint industry, waterproofing agent for fabrics, thickening agent for lubricating oil, etc. It is insoluble in water, ethanol, ether, but soluble in solvents such as alkali, turpentine, mineral oil, petroleum, kerosene, and benzene. It forms a thixotropic gel on heating with mineral oils and solvents which is the main premise of its use and design. We have hi-gel, supergel and non-gel grades. We manufacture all three types-&nbsp;<strong>aluminium mono-stearate, aluminium di-stearate and aluminium tri-stearate</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Special Features Of Our Aluminium Stearate</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Very high gelling power. Forms strong gel even at as low as 1.5-2.0% dosage</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Moisture depletes gelling power. Our aluminium stearate has a very controlled moisture due to twin stage automatic drying system.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Manufactured in a dedicated plant, therefore, there are zero contaminants present, like zinc or calcium, which are gel breakers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose Us As Your Aluminium Stearate Suppliers?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Since its establishment, MLA Group of Industries has always regarded product quality as the core of the company&#39;s participation in market competition. It is this successful positioning and our employees&#39; sound management and a strong awareness of the product quality that makes us professional&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate suppliers</strong>. We are a &quot;customer first&quot; company who strongly believe that our success depends on our product quality and the satisfaction of our customers. To this end, we work closely with every customer to support high-quality business services. The modern warehousing and advanced logistics system ensure the safety of chemicals and quick and timely delivery to customers. We are, thus, regarded as one of the most reputed&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate exporters in the World</strong>, with strong comprehensive strength in R&amp;D and marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Our strengths include :</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>A) In house fabrication and erection</li>\r\n	<li>B) DSIR recognized in house R&amp;D equipped with laser particle size analyzer, BET surface area analyzer, etc</li>\r\n	<li>C) In house plastic laboratory equipped with a rheometer, VR testing, two roll, etc</li>\r\n	<li>D) The three-tier quality control system</li>\r\n	<li>E) Fast decision making due to the flat structure</li>\r\n	<li>F) Customer-driven &ndash; strong complaint handling system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At MLA Group, we promise reasonable prices, a short supply cy<strong>cle, and satisfactory after-sales service.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>What is the benefit of using Aluminium Stearate?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Aluminium Stearate is mainly used as gelling agent, used in the manufacturing of grease, oil drilling chemicals, explosives, water proofing of canvas in combination with paraffin wax and also as an anti-selling agent in paints. It also finds use as a gelling agent in pharmaceutical and cosmetic preparations for which we manufacture pharma grade product also. As a&nbsp;<strong>leading Aluminium Stearate exporters in India</strong>, we strictly control and manage all links related to product quality, establish scientific inspection standards, and ensure that the company maintains stable and qualified products.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Where can I purchase premium quality aluminium stearate for industrial purposes?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are looking for industrial-grade aluminum stearate, consider MLA Group as your&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate suppliers</strong>. In India, we are currently one of the&nbsp;<strong>leading Aluminium Stearate manufacturers</strong>. We continue to innovate around the needs and requirements of our customers and we believe in open cooperation with partners. We are committed to providing scientific research with competitive comprehensive solutions and services, continuously improving customer experience, and creating maximum value for customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What type of aluminium stearate do you supply?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As one of the<strong>&nbsp;Aluminium Stearate manufacturers in the World</strong>, at MLA Group, we provide fine quality Aluminium Stearate, available in different forms as per the needs of our customers. Our product, a white fine powder with moisture level less than 2 percent, is stored in fine conditions, out of human touch. We develop them using effective technology backed with strong scientific research. These chemicals are tested on several different quality standards and are inspected strictly in accordance with the procedures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<h3>Applications</h3>\n<p>Our professionalism has promoted our rapid development and satisfied our domestic and foreign customers, making us a popular name among&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate suppliers</strong>&nbsp;not only in&nbsp;<strong>India</strong>&nbsp;but also&nbsp;<strong>in the world</strong>. We export premium quality metallic stearates to 46 countries, around every corner of the globe.</p>\n\n<h3>Uses of Aluminium Stearate include:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>&nbsp;Increasing viscosity in greases (especially graphite grease)</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;Form waterproof coating along with wax for canvas fabric coating (eg., boots, military tents, wtc.)</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;When heated, it forms a gel with mineral oil, hence, acts as an anti-setting agent by forming a thixotropic gel in solvent-based paints.</li>\n	<li>As a gelling agent in many cosmetic formulations.</li>\n</ul>\n', '2024-04-25 08:06:31', '2024-11-06 10:38:17'),
(63, 'Calcium Zinc Stabilizer', 'calcium-zinc-stabilizer-manufacturers', 'Leading Calcium zinc stabilizer manufacturers & suppliers', 'MLA Group is the leading manufacturing & supplying company of Calcium zinc stabilizer from the last 44 years. We are world-class exporter of zinc stabilizer.', '<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n	{\r\n	  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n	  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\r\n	  \"mainEntity\": [{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"What is the use of calcium zinc stabilizers?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>The use of calcium zinc stabilizers has been common in PVC. They are widely used in many flexible and rigid PVC applications because of the characteristics of calcium zinc stabilized materials. Such stabilizing systems give products that have a high degree of clarity, good mechanical and electrical properties, excellent organoleptic properties, and good outdoor weather ability.</p> \"\r\n		}\r\n	  },{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"Where can I purchase industrial grade calcium zinc stabilizers? \",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>MLA Group of industries is a leading name as<b> Calcium zinc stabilizer suppliers in India.</b> We have amassed some reputable clients over a period of years who would vouch for our product quality and the economical prices. The company is now one of the leading exporters of calcium zinc stabilizers at the national & international levels.</p> \"\r\n		}\r\n	  },{\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"Are calcium zinc stabilizers safe to use?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p>Calcium zinc stabilizers are non-toxic PVC heat stabilizers that pose no risks to human health or the environment. In fact, the use of calcium/zinc stabilizer systems has been common in PVC applications in the past few decades and are widely used in many flexible and rigid PVC applications.</p>\"  \r\n		}\r\n	  }]\r\n	}\r\n	</script>', 'product-image/CZ.webp', '', '23', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Calcium zinc stabilizer suppliers in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is one of the world&rsquo;s leading manufacturers and suppliers of Calcium zinc stabilizer, and a trending name in both national and international markets. As a global leader, we are committed to providing superior quality heat stabilizers that include lead-free&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/pvc-heat-stabilizers-manufacturers.html\">PVC stabilizers</a>&nbsp;i.e., Calcium-Zinc based complex non-toxic stabilizers at competitive market prices. These stabilizers are ever evolving and with our in-house PVC lab and application centre, we carry out continuous research to improve existing products and develop new grades. With a production capacity of more than 1000 tons per month, we cater to a large segment of industries and have formed long term associations with many leading names in the industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product - Calcium Zinc Stabilizer</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Calcium zinc stabilizers are a complex mixture of over 10-15 ingredients like stearates, organic stabilizers, inorganic stabilizers, antioxidants, lubricants, fillers, etc. It is a non-toxic stabilizer that is the preferred choice over lead-based stabilizers which are completely banned in developed countries and slowly being phased out of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Special Features of Our Calcium Zinc Stabilizer</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As the global leaders of today, and a well-known name among&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/calcium-stearate-manufacturers.html\">Calcium Stearate</a>&nbsp;suppliers in the world&nbsp;</strong>, we are committed to developing high-quality calcium steerates that have the following unique properties:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;High heat stability</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Processing fluidity and ease</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;ILubricating ability</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Effective performance as per the need of the product ( customization )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose Us as Your Calcium Zinc Stabilizer Suppliers in India?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group Of Industries, we pride in our research &amp; development facilities that have helped us benchmark our products along the lines of international quality yet offering them at cost-effective prices to our customers, thereby, establishing ourselves as one of the&nbsp;<strong>leading calcium zinc stabilizer manufacturers and suppliers in India.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not limited to geographical boundaries, we export to over 46 countries around every corner of the globe making us a leading name among Calcium zinc stabilizer exporters in India. With a huge investment in modern production, and stable quality and timely delivery, we are committed to becoming a model enterprise on a global scale.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our strengths lie in our</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>A)</em>&nbsp;In house fabrication and erection</li>\r\n	<li><em>B)&nbsp;</em>DSIR recognized in house R&amp;D equipped with laser particle size analyzer, BET surface area analyzer, etc</li>\r\n	<li><em>C)&nbsp;</em>In house plastic laboratory equipped with a rheometer, VR testing, two rolls, etc</li>\r\n	<li><em>D)</em>&nbsp;The three-tier quality control system</li>\r\n	<li><em>E)&nbsp;</em>Fast decision making due to the flat structure</li>\r\n	<li><em>F)&nbsp;</em>Customer-driven &ndash; strong complaint handling system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Technical Support</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group Of Industries, we have in-house application labs with plastic and technology experts available for research and providing round the clock technical services to our clients. We can participate in your product development and production according to your needs, analyze the problems you encounter, and provide you with effective technical solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>What is the use of calcium zinc stabilizers?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The use of calcium zinc stabilizers has been common in PVC. They are widely used in many flexible and rigid PVC applications because of the characteristics of calcium zinc stabilized materials. Such stabilizing systems give products that have a high degree of clarity, good mechanical and electrical properties, excellent organoleptic properties, and good outdoor weather ability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Where can I purchase industrial grade calcium zinc stabilizers?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of industries is a leading name as<strong>&nbsp;Calcium zinc stabilizer suppliers in India.</strong>&nbsp;We have amassed some reputable clients over a period of years who would vouch for our product quality and the economical prices. The company is now one of the leading exporters of calcium zinc stabilizers at the national &amp; international levels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are calcium zinc stabilizers safe to use?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Calcium zinc stabilizers are non-toxic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/pvc-heat-stabilizers-manufacturers.html\">PVC heat stabilizers</a>&nbsp;that pose no risks to human health or the environment. In fact, the use of calcium/zinc stabilizer systems has been common in PVC applications in the past few decades and are widely used in many flexible and rigid PVC applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<h3>Applications</h3>\n<p>MLA Industries is a&nbsp;<strong>leading exporter</strong>&nbsp;of a wide range of&nbsp;<strong>Calcium Zinc Stabilizer&nbsp;</strong>extensively used for Pipes, Profiles, Cable, Footwear, etc, manufactured using only the finest materials conforming to stringent quality norms.</p>\n\n<p>Our Calcium Zinc Stabilizer is used in :</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>In the cable industry or plasticized PVC ( 40-50 phr of plasticizers like DOP, DBP, TOTM, CPW, etc ) the grades are developed to give a good:</li>\n	<li>Static stability (color of PVC compound at 180C for different times, Tikki test, a chart of color deterioration with time is prepared )</li>\n	<li>Thermal stability ( congo-red time or time taken for the PVC compound to decompose )</li>\n	<li>Volume resistivity, the wet VR etc ( electrical properties ) Special grades for HVAC and HVDC cables</li>\n	<li>Color holding ( uncured compound should not change color with ageing ).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>For this, we have a full-fledged PVC lab to check the performance of our various grades. The grades are defined on the basis of the service temperature of the cable and can be 70, 90, 105, or 125 degrees C. We accordingly have grades CZ-815, CZ-835, CZ-55, CZ-75, CZ-889, and many others as per the specific requirement of clients.</p>\n\n<p>In the pipe industry, which is unplasticized, hard, or rigid. The stabilizer is developed to give good stability and smooth flow through the extruder. This is done by static heat stability test, Rheometer test to check flow and stability properties, and through checking the load in actual extrusion on a pilot or full-scale plant. We have many grades including CZ-RP40 against Sunace 911 and CZ-321-P against more recent grade 3210 of Baerlocher. We also have economy grades like RP-20 for WPC and other applications like marble flooring.</p>\n', '2024-04-25 08:12:12', '2024-11-06 10:38:23'),
